    {
      "parameters": {
        "content": "## HINDSIGHT \u2014 postmortem intelligence pipeline\nDrop a postmortem (.pdf/.docx/.md) into **/data/incoming_docs**.\nGemini extracts an SRE schema \u2192 FastAPI re-scores severity, routes to the owning team, computes error-budget burn & a recurrence fingerprint \u2192 Sheets + Gmail.",
        "height": 180,
        "width": 540,
        "color": 4
      },
      "id": "ce4a6e29-a9a5-4ef7-9232-08ec11cffca2",
      "name": "Note 1f8da0",
      "type": "n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote",
      "typeVersion": 1,
      "position": [
        180,
        70
      ]
    },
    {
      "parameters": {
        "content": "### Multimodal branch\nIf the doc embeds a Grafana/dashboard image, Gemini Vision reads the chart and the notes are folded into the main extraction. `onError: continue` so a vision miss never blocks the pipeline.",
        "height": 150,
        "width": 300,
        "color": 5
      },
      "id": "c8d620f0-99fc-4688-9a5e-89d84a754ca0",
      "name": "Note b30625",
      "type": "n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote",
      "typeVersion": 1,
      "position": [
        1220,
        -60
      ]
    },
    {
      "parameters": {
        "content": "### Severity is computed, not trusted\nThe FastAPI service re-scores severity from a rubric (service tier \u00d7 jurisdiction breadth \u00d7 impact language). SEV1 \u2192 immediate page.",
        "height": 130,
        "width": 320,
        "color": 3
      },
      "id": "f29c7b84-c7c8-4560-805c-d7e5e1b5c828",
      "name": "Note 9f34cc",
